sentences: José Ramón Tebar Sáiz (November 6, 1978, Valencia, Spain) is a conductor and pianist, currently Principal Conductor at Florida Grand Opera.
He is Artistic Director of Opera Naples.
He was Music Director of the Festival of Santo Domingo, Dominican Republic (2009-2015).
In March 2015, he was named Principal Guest Conductor of Spain's Palau de les Arts Reina Sofia.
